{"tid":964056,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"［恐怖］比鬼壓有預知？！","createTime":"2019-01-01T04:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T03:05:42.000Z","uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6b8223932a2bea8324470d70000de05efbd9a4f9","tid":964056,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:08:20.000Z","msg":"啱啱發生咗件我覺得幾恐怖嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我訓教嘅姿勢係身向天，臉向右手邊（右邊牆嚟嘅）<br />\n我嗰時嘅狀態係已經半醒左，但合埋眼嘅狀態（類似想訓，但合埋眼，而已經準備進入睡眠狀態咁）<br />\n個腦嗰時閃過一個畫面就係我搭電梯上去一個地方，之後我就趴喺地下爬過啲樹（樹上面有啲蜜蜂，而啲樹生得好斜，所以要爬過）之後我好似撞到個蜜蜂「鬥」，咁我就勁驚，即刻走［向後咁行，臉向前］中途我就kick到嘢從高處跌落街。<br />\n之後我眼前就出現左個細細哋嘅人影係訓喺度嘅（臉同身都向天嘅）格1-2秒個影開始閃，愈閃愈密，愈閃愈快！呢個時候，我後腦就有啲嘢掃咗一掃，整咗我一下，同一時間個人影消失左。<br />\n格咗一至兩秒，諗住想擰返個頭去前面，點知郁唔到！出哂力都郁唔到！又格咗3-4秒後，咁就先郁得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我第一次發生呢啲事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2019-1-1<br />\n<br />\nQ:<br />\n1.我見到嘅人影係咪即係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n2.佢係咁閃，一閃完就消失，跟住我後腦就feel到有嘢整我係咪即係預先話我知有嘢入嚟我身體？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3.我係咪真係比鬼壓定係咩睡眠癱瘓症？"},{"pid":"80d70390085587323baba5cc06c18666342a5b09","tid":964056,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f280a80c4d300836f841ede914169f2efddea96","tid":964056,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:54:39.000Z","msg":"真事嚟 做咩要比負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d338bff05f5f3ec72ec0470f1fd1e62d008844c","tid":964056,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:59:18.000Z","msg":"我本身有焦慮症醫生話可能關事<br />\n奇就奇起我食過ADHD藥提升dopamine結果嗰排成日俾鬼壓 一日幾次 後尾停藥<br />\n之後有隻焦慮藥減低dopamine就冇在發生 一次都冇"},{"pid":"6714d5ab002ba8bfe62f1d8dc2b68dfe263a3ae7","tid":964056,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d338bff05f5f3ec72ec0470f1fd1e62d008844c","tid":964056,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:59:18.000Z","msg":"我本身有焦慮症醫生話可能關事<br />\n奇就奇起我食過ADHD藥提升dopamine結果嗰排成日俾鬼壓 一日幾次 後尾停藥<br />\n之後有隻焦慮藥減低dopamine就冇在發生 一次都冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多dopamine 會比鬼壓<br />\n我就冇焦慮症⋯"},{"pid":"1b5997c918d47a1b28bf1bc89deb2e5cc1ec6837","tid":964056,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb04f07a755a6ad50bd30863505a74b18b357755","tid":964056,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想知"},{"pid":"ba0419772f2910620f7129a3e76cd5dec16723b2","tid":964056,"uid":194876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"睡眠癱瘓症啦<br />\n有撚咁多鬼<br />\n<br />\n利申：成日睡眠癱瘓症"},{"pid":"804e00616ec7b337617c9f4edc17d548407395fb","tid":964056,"uid":61991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T07:12:50.000Z","msg":"認真，google查下睡眠癱瘓症同清醒夢已經解釋到你所有問題，你自己睇好過我話你知。"},{"pid":"bfa17f3a2bbf43786069939798876f72688e8312","tid":964056,"uid":107217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T07:27:28.000Z","msg":"我兩年前有半年成日比鬼壓，壓前既預兆就係耳嗚，有一次直頭有聲起我耳邊，跟住病左獲金訓左一星期醫院就冇再壓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11cfcd41f95fa22ff7d42ca29127b45e603de0cf","tid":964056,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfa17f3a2bbf43786069939798876f72688e8312","tid":9